author: Glen Yu
title: Cloud & AI/ML announcements at Google I/O 2023
description: I had the incredible opportunity to attend Google I/O, the highly anticipated annual developer conference held at Shoreline Amphitheatre. Being present in person allowed me to immerse myself in the excitement of live announcements and festivities. Throughout the event, numerous captivating announcements were made, with a significant focus on AI/ML advancements. In the coming recap, I will highlight some of the most intriguing announcements, showcasing the innovative developments unveiled at Google I/O.
